`Fib[2] = Fib[0] + Fib[1];` this should be `Fib[i] = Fib[i - 1] + Fib[i - 2];`   
Another mistake is nesting for loops. The enhanced for loop should be after the loop with index `i`. 

    int[] Fib = new int[20];
