      &lt;version&gt;2.0.0-RC1&lt;/version&gt;
      &lt;scope&gt;provided&lt;/scope&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;
```

Since Servlet 3.0, additional Jakarta EE specifications can be added using the [servlet pluggability mechanism](https://jakarta.ee/specifications/servlet/5.0/jakarta-servlet-spec-5.0.html#shared-libraries-runtimes-pluggability). To use JAX-RS you need to add:

```lang-xml
&lt;dependency&gt;
